main event: Observers reported seeing multiple bright white and green objects in the sky while airborne over Guam.
interesting points: The observation lasted between 10 to 15 minutes., A total of 10 objects were seen during the sighting., One object emitted a pulsating red tail before burning out., Observations were made by credible military personnel aboard a Navy aircraft., The objects were estimated to be traveling at speeds of 200-300 mph.
sighted object: bright white and green burning objects
witness description: William L. Parks, CDR, USN and John W. Hammond, LCDR, USN, both from AEWRON ONE
